      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GO BARBARA (8) is a first starter from the Matthew Clark yard by My Redeemer out of Xanadu. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Strong market watch advised but profiles nicely for this. DEEP TALENT (2) is yet to break through in 18 starts but has run a number of placings. Was below best latest when fifth (25.11) at this track but did hit the frame the start prior. Great chance to atone. ASTON TARZAN (4) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing sixth (26.16) at this track in a Maiden H. Can hit the frame this time. RIO BON BON (6) did a good job to finish second last time out over 350m at Traralgon (20.78) in a Maiden, the second top-three finish on the trot.",
